'''Dan Hennessey''' was a voice actor who played [[Jord Dusat]], Uncle [[Putch Gundarian|Gundy]], [[Jyn Obah]], [[Vinga]], and [[Yorpo Mog|Yorpo]] on [[Star Wars: Droids: The Adventures of R2-D2 and C-3PO|''Star Wars Droids'']]; and King [[Gorneesh/Legends|Gorneesh]] on [[Ewoks (television series)|''Ewoks'']].

